runpath.description: The shared object does not have RUNPATH set.

fortify.description: The shared object does not have any fortified functions. Fortified functions provides buffer overflow checks against glibc's commons insecure functions like strcpy, gets etc. Use the compiler option -D_FORTIFY_SOURCE=2 to fortify functions.

playstore_details.title: Bitcoin, Cryptocurrency & Blockchain News
playstore_details.description:
Your trusted stop for all cryptocurrency news!

Get connected and become an expert on the new economy. This app brings you the latest and most relevant updates about Bitcoin, Bitcoin Cash, Ethereum, Litecoin, Monero, Ripple, Cardano, IOTA, EOS, ZCash, and other cryptocurrencies/blockchain assets.
We also cover the latest ICOs, token sales and dapps (distributed apps).
In addition, we cover bitcoin trading and the various exchanges - from Coinbase/GDAX to Kraken, Gemini, Binance, Bithumb, Poloniex, Bitfinex, Bittrex, BitMEX, Luno and others.

We only deliver articles from leading news sources all around the web. We and our algorithms work hard so you don't have to.

Here's what you get in the app:

 - Full coverage - dozens of news sources in one app, posting solely about crypto and digital currencies. You get a full coverage from all over the web, with no unrelated articles. Get a clean, prioritized feed - the most important news appear first and no repeated stories! 

- Push notifications - Allow us to keep you up to date! Whenever something really important is happening, we will send you a push notification to let you know about it (optional)!

- Topic management - choose your favorite topics, block certain topics and choose the topics you want to get notifications about! Read only what you want, get notified on only what interests you, and the configuration is easy and quick!

- Join the community! Post stories or polls, comment on stories, tag articles and earn badges!

- Read later - save interesting stories for later reading inside the app.

- Blocking unwanted sources - you can now filter-out entirely any source you don't want in featured in the app!

- Collapsed mode - a mode that allows you to skim through the news quickly and efficiently and decide what you want to read!
Loved the app? Let us know by rating it high and sharing it with your friends!

Use of the Newsfusion Application is governed by the Newsfusion Terms of Use (http://newsfusion.com/terms-privacy-policy).
